Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.13,0:00:08.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上…热
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.21,0:00:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上热
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.72,0:00:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热啊  超热的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.77,0:00:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  有必要说这么多次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.05,0:00:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超想马上回家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊好可笑呢  超可笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而觉得奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年暑假去海边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去游泳池就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不一样的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意义完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了害羞了吗  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.59,0:00:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在众目睽睽之下自己释放出内心奔放的情绪是很害羞的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  看小唯最多的肯定是我们！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:27.10,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,590)\fad(500,500)}No event  Good life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.06,0:02:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.65,0:02:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年去海边了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.76,0:02:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没有去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只去了游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有提议说去  但是相川她不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想带小相去海边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超想带她去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超想带她去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳衣是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.49,0:02:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那种一边黑  一边黑白相间的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比基尼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:02:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小相呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有相川风格  泳衣下面是那种飘飘然的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.17,0:03:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想带她去转转
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超想带她去转转
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  这是我家的相川
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:18.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年日向家的夏季家族旅行已经计划好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.06,0:03:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  好像没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我有说过想和柚子还有小唯一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说万一出了事负不起责任  所以不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是去国外嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.55,0:03:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这么大了  也不会出事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:39.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的暑假没有任何回忆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么不好的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回忆下去年的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有各种各样的回忆不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愉快的夏天  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没死呢  今年的暑假也要好好享受哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天也一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最享受的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后明天的享受就是明天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再说美好的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么美好的事情…等等小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么很美好了你还一副生气的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美好点有什么不好 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯可是相当美好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  老娘不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我没生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗  那真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  她并没有生气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想去海边而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海边？不错啊海边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是暑假嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:08.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}柚子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:08.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:08.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}今天去小唯家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢生气的语气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家现在有圆圆的西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不给你们吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这样捉弄我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我只是觉得很有趣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快道歉一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥…我说了捉弄你们的话  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把西瓜端上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是老板娘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来我家也有冰激凌  2升特大的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:53.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的啊  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:06:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  你知道我现在最想要的是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰激凌吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那现在吃了冰激凌就？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就说要冰激凌不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们去KI…厨房吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KI？你刚想说kitchen的吧  为啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去厨房吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯有果酱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！这提议好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有草莓酱和橘皮果酱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缘同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然想去厕所了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去厕所吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:06:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱玩冰箱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天开始你就住在这里面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃冰激凌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果酱真好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果酱真好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果酱…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厕所借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.53,0:07:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里住一辈子也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滚回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说西瓜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去厕所啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种…有种想要敲点东西的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐不住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要兴奋起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.39,0:08:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小缘你是困了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要先回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我以为你是刚被人甩了的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个孩子总有天也会和谁结婚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是她爸爸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缘过上幸福的生活  收入稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时正经  偶尔不正经
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不贪心  身体健康的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求好多啊  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去便利店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:08:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给小缘买点什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷饮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗  乱花零花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天才刚刚开始哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦  用在你们身上不算乱花啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话我说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿再问缘要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天变长了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.63,0:09:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短信  冈野同学来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发短信的对象  好像已经确定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小相还有小缘和小文
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳池超开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.53,0:09:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊泳池  海边就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我流口水了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把枕头弄湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了  有什么烦恼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流口水了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你一个人大哭了一场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在小唯家是不会哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在小唯家也不会哭  而且还超那啥的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:37.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂可爱吗  我们可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很那啥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别靠过来  是哪个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多爱我们一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友吗  哪有不爱你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不够啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  我回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸头摸头  快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠悠式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好困
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊  其实我也有点困哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是一样的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要跑步就会累哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是一样的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要被刀刺到的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我避开啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.93,0:11:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好正确
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要放屁…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快散开啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要进入被子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要吃到鹅肝的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说我不知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼子酱呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:55.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河豚刺身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:11:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有木乃伊博物馆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.31,0:12:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木乃伊的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是说好几个贵的东西之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说点便宜的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你看  已经暴露了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么关于最喜欢的食物的话题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小唯你最喜欢的鱼翅料理是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  接下来要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去海边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在去肯定晚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉什么都不想做了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要抱我的枕头啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么去海边什么都不做怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.37,0:12:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:42.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢你个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯你赶紧换泳衣  现在在这里换
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在什么都不会做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是心口不一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿去年那件白的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:13:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要嘛  而且也不合身了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新学期的体检数据呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是突然地长了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体检的时候表现出的那种连带感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然长大原来不是都市传说什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:19.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小唯  让我稍微验证一下你的秘密能量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.06,0:13:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们给我回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:26.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你们得感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你们连续两天丢失两三千円
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你们租到满是刮痕的DVD  还要拖欠租期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.42,0:13:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你们所有的汤都打翻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:39.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都打翻在床上吧  猪骨汤之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  至于说那么多？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯真的喜欢我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.71,0:13:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  喜欢喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜欢小唯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.22,0:13:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是不怵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要小唯这样的笑着  就觉得够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊这是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  外面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是外面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是完全的外面了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是完全的外面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全的外面是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就别在意这个了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也去海边吧  我说真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  在暑假的期间去海边已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不感到害羞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊你看  春天还不是要去赏花吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天去滑雪之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:14:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？我们什么都没做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去海边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  夏天来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是别去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小唯的背后好没有防备啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防备啊  真是疏于防备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个在召唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没在召唤我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯啊  你摆出一副欲求不满的后背还要对我生气是要怎样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯有的时候就是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  还真有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还想让你再说出一次「谁知道啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果什么也没想出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海母亲！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热好热
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉海水的感觉好不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.27,0:16:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:17:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  这…这…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.24,0:17:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉慢慢变得不那么差了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去那个球那里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是好远
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说小缘  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国外的海水和日本的海水有什么不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国外的海呢  雪白的沙滩透着海水的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后日本的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有小唯和柚子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  裙带菜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积雨云！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  让我骑一下肩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼  好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑死了  刚才的好好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来猜拳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好弱！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好弱！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多的沙滩伞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙滩伞…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香蕉船…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这说法…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:56.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是传说中的海之家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:19:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在Max想吃的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  Max想的  Max想的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像会有叫「Max海风」的海之家不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇…好土啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Sunshine海风」之类的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「广岛三箭」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:20.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}广岛三箭：日本甲级足球俱乐部之一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长谷川蒙古手刀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:23.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}蒙古手刀：原摔跤手Killer Khan的格斗特技之一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格斗特技吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山形蒙迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}山形蒙迪奥：也是日本甲级足球俱乐部之一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又回到足球了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  笑饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉回家好麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.43,0:19:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家好麻烦噢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上快开学了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和有没有放假没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅是为了被宠爱而活着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在外面也光着身子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来好好爱你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.37,0:20:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.86,0:20:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？姐姐在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.56,0:20:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  冰激凌没了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  今天去买东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  想要冰激凌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？为啥你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.97,0:20:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去买啦  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:02.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我不吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的在当班长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.99,0:21:27.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是柚子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙滩伞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.86,0:21:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发硬邦邦的  是晒伤了么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.02,0:21:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮肤好热
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.51,0:21:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前因为害羞不想去  真像个笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.00,0:21:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.31,0:22:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就要开学了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.74,0:22:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在想想我们还上学的时候  刚放假完那几天真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.32,0:22:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很辛苦  但我觉得慢慢变好了  当老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.18,0:22:19.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.82,0:22:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 比起学生时代  变得没有那么讨厌开学了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.84,0:22:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.72,0:22:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.03,0:22:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  柚子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.54,0:22:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.48,0:22:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  柚子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.42,0:22:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.49,0:22:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.02,0:22:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是很热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:22:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还是夏天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.45,0:22:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想去海边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.13,0:23:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经去过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.51,0:23:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.47,0:23:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.60,0:23:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.35,0:23:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.96,0:23:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海边很好玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.87,0:23:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么  难道说小唯对开放的环境觉醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你闭嘴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.90,0:23:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.35,0:23:22.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啦  小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
